 a natural swimming pool, making it the perfect place for a swim. Plus, it&#x2019;s an excellent place to see giant turtles; look out for their little heads poking up above the water for some air.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-fisherman-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"7373\" class=\"wp-image-7373 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154427\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-fisherman-2.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154427\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-fisherman-2-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154427\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-fisherman-2-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154427\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-fisherman-2-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154427\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-fisherman-2-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154427\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-fisherman-2-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154427\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-fisherman-2-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154427\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-fisherman-2-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154427\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-fisherman-2-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinour