er-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155035\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-coconut-tree-header-338x338.jpg 338w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155035\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-coconut-tree-header-30x30.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155035\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-coconut-tree-header-163x163.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155035\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-coconut-tree-header-180x180.jpg 180w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155035\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-coconut-tree-header-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155035\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-coconut-tree-header-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155035\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-coconut-tree-header-1080x1080.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155035\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-coconut-tree-header-1440x1440.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155035\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-coconut-tree-header.jpg 1920w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155035\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-coconut-tree-header-30x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155035\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-coconut-tree-header-810x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Parrot Rock (although you won&#x2019;t find parrots!) is a great thing to do while you&#x2019;re visiting Mirissa Beach. The rock sits in front of the beach and offers great views of the palm tree forest below. Because the rock is out at sea, you&#x2019;ll need to research tidal times to walk across safely.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/mirissa\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">11 Great Things To Do in Mirissa<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Season:<\/strong> November to April and August to October<\/li><li><strong>Crowded:<\/strong> Quite popular. Parrot Rock is particularly busy at sunset. We recommend visiting at sunrise (if the tide permits) for a quieter viewing experience.&#xA0;<\/li><li><strong>Surfing:<\/strong> Good surfing to the right of Parrot Rock.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-parrot-rock.jpg\" alt=\"sri lanka beaches mirissa parrot rock\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"303\" alt=\"sri lanka beaches mirissa parrot rock\" class=\"wp-image-6889 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/