a-secret-beach-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155115\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155115\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155115\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/23155115\/Things-To-Do-Mirissa-Sri-Lanka-secret-beach.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you get there, you&#x2019;ll see the headland is split into three little beaches. Each one is a little bit different and it&#x2019;s an excellent place for snorkeling and sunsets. If you get here early enough in the morning, you&#x2019;ll likely get to enjoy this beautiful ocean paradise completely alone!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/mirissa\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">11 Great Things To Do in Mirissa<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Season:<\/strong> November to April and August to October<\/li><li><strong>Crowded<\/strong>: A bit crowded later on in the day, but arrive early, and you&#x2019;ll get to enjoy it for yourself.<\/li><li><strong>Surfing:<\/strong> Not great, better for paddling in the rock pools and enjoying the snorkeling.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n\n    <a class=\"ebook-banner ebook-banner--sl\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/shop\/ebooks\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n        <img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" data-src=\"\/build\/images\/ebooks\/traveling-sri-lanka\/slebook-banner.jpg\" class=\"lazypreload\" height=\"225\" width=\"800\" alt=\"Ebook Sri Lanka\">\n    <\/a>\n    \n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-4-hiriketiya-beach-in-sri-lanka\">4. Hiriketiya Beach in Sri Lanka<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Hiriketiya Beach, also called Hiri Beach, is becoming more famous for its waves. Some say it&#x2019;s fast becoming the surfer&#x2019;s paradise of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a>! It&#x2019;s easy to see why the horseshoe bay is so popular, backed by dense palm tree forest, and close to trendy eateries where you can get a delicious brunch. Surfers are drawn to this spot from all over the world, bringing with them a surfy, bohemian vibe that can be seen throughout Hiriketiya.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/hiriketiya-dikwella\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Dikwella, the Surf &amp; Beach Gem of Sri Lanka<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/23132136\/things-to-do-dikwella-1039x810.jpg\" alt=\"things to do dikwella\"><\/noscript><img width=\"434\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do dikwella\" data-id=\"16425\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/23132136\/things-to-do-dikwella.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/things-to-do-dikwella\/\" class=\"wp-image-16425 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1039px) 100vw, 1039px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/23132136\/things-to-do-dikwella-1039x810.jpg 1039w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/23132136\/things-to-do-dikwella-300x234.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/23132136\/things-to-do-dikwella-600x468.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/23132136\/things-to-do-dikwella-434x338.jpg 434w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/23132136\/things-to-do-dikwella-770x600.jpg 770w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/23132136\/things-to-do-dikwella-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/23132136\/things-to-do-dikwella-163x127.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/23132136\/things-to-do-dikwella-231x180.jpg 231w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/23132136\/things-to-do-dikwella-768x599.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\