tiya-Dikwella-palm-swing-header.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-5-trincomalee-beach\">5. Trincomalee Beach<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Trincomalee Beach and Nilaveli Beach are entirely different from other Sri Lanka beaches. Because of their location, off the beaten track on the east coast, you&#x2019;ll find these beaches almost empty. Plus, the scenery is breathtaking.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Trincomalee beach is a little busier, filled with traditional, colorful fishing boats and locals casting their nets just off the shore. You&#x2019;ll also find some great beach bars here, where you can sit on swings and choose from many refreshing cocktails.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/trincomalee\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">7 Things To Do Trincomalee<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/23153838\/things-to-do-trincomalee-main-beach.jpg\" alt=\"best beaches in Sri Lanka\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"311\" alt=\"best beaches in Sri Lanka\" class=\"wp-image-7650 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/23153838\/things-to-do-trincomalee-main-beach.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.