omalee-sri-lanka-nilaveli-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/23154137\/things-do-to-trincomalee-sri-lanka-nilaveli-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/23154137\/things-do-to-trincomalee-sri-lanka-nilaveli-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/23154137\/things-do-to-trincomalee-sri-lanka-nilaveli-593x768.jpg 593w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/23154137\/things-do-to-trincomalee-sri-lanka-nilaveli-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/23154137\/things-do-to-trincomalee-sri-lanka-nilaveli-834x1080.jpg 834w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/23154137\/things-do-to-trincomalee-sri-lanka-nilaveli-1112x1440.jpg 1112w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/23154137\/things-do-to-trincomalee-sri-lanka-nilaveli-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/23154137\/things-do-to-trincomalee-sri-lanka-nilaveli.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-6-tangalle-beach\">6. Tangalle Beach<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Hidden on the south-eastern coast, Tangalle is one of those Sri Lanka beaches made for paradise seekers. It&#x2019;s a bit harder to reach as it&#x2019;s dislocated from the usual <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/sri-lanka-route-guide\/\">Sri Lanka route<\/a> but so worth a visit! This means that few tourists visit Tangalle, creating a more tranquil experience (you&#x2019;ll notice that the area only contains a handful of visible resorts).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/sri-lanka-beaches-tangalle-drone.jpg\" alt=\"sri lanka beaches tangalle drone\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sri lanka beaches tangalle drone\" class=\"wp-image-7555 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154044\/sri-lanka-beaches-tangalle-drone.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154044\/sri-lanka-beaches-tangalle-drone-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154044\/sri-lanka-beaches-tangalle-drone-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154044\/sri-lanka-beaches-tangalle-drone-450x338.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154044\/sri-lanka-beaches-tangalle-drone-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154044\/sri-lanka-beaches-tangalle-drone-1080x810.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154044\/sri-lanka-beaches-tangalle-drone-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154044\/sri-lanka-beaches-tangalle-drone-163x122.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154044\/sri-lanka-beaches-tangalle-drone-240x180.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154044\/sri-lanka-beaches-tangalle-drone-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154044\/sri-lanka-beaches-tangalle-drone-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154044\/sri-lanka-beaches-tangalle-drone-1440x1080.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154044\/sri-lanka-beaches-tangalle-drone-30x23.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154044\/sri-lanka-beaches-tangalle-drone.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4>Best hidden beach of Sri Lanka<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The traditional fishing village is home to the friendliest people and gorgeous white sand beaches, surrounded by turquoise ocean, large frothy waves, and palm-tree and mangrove groves. Because of the reef and rocks, there is a strong current and big waves, which make Tangalle beach unsuitable for swimming and surfing. However, the long beach is perfect for walks, relaxing, and a fantastic place to watch the sun go down.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Enjoy the peaceful sounds of nature, sleep in the shade of the trees, and get your fill of fresh coconuts from passing sellers. A trip to Tangalle is an absolute must on your journey through Sri Lanka!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Silent beach is the best beach in the area, tranquil, with picture-perfect scenery &#x2013; one of the most fantastic <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a> beaches.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Season:<\/strong> November to April and May through October<\/li><li><strong>Crowded:<\/strong> Very quiet!<\/li><li><strong>Surfing:<\/strong> Not for surfing. Swimming can also be difficult here, especially in September and October.&#xA0;<\/li><\/ul>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-7-koggala-beach\">7. Koggala Beach<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Koggala is a relatively unknown beach paradise in the deep Southwest of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a>, located between <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/unawatuna\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Unawatuna<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/mirissa\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Mirissa<\/a>. The white sand and the few people on the beach make Koggala beach a great location to stay on your trip. Spend your days creating the first footprints in the sand and watching the fantastic variety of wildlife here, from colorful fish to turtles and even small sharks!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/sri-lanka-beaches-koggala-coconuts.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"7546\" class=\"wp-image-7546 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154059\/sri-lanka-beaches-koggala-coconuts.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154059\/sri-lanka-beaches-koggala-coconuts-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154059\/sri-lanka-beaches-koggala-coconuts-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154059\/sri-lanka-beaches-koggala-coconuts-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154059\/sri-lanka-beaches-koggala-coconuts-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154059\/sri-lanka-beaches-koggala-coconuts-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154059\/sri-lanka-beaches-koggala-coconuts-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154059\/sri-lanka-beaches-koggala-coconuts-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154059\/sri-lanka-beaches-koggala-coconuts-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154059\/sri-lanka-beaches-koggala-coconuts-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154059\/sri-lanka-beaches-koggala-coconuts-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154059\/sri-lanka-beaches-koggala-coconuts-835x1080.jpg 835w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154059\/sri-lanka-beaches-koggala-coconuts-1113x1440.jpg 1113w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154059\/sri-lanka-beaches-koggala-coconuts-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror