i-lanka-beaches-koggala-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154055\/sri-lanka-beaches-koggala-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154055\/sri-lanka-beaches-koggala-835x1080.jpg 835w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154055\/sri-lanka-beaches-koggala-1113x1440.jpg 1113w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154055\/sri-lanka-beaches-koggala-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154055\/sri-lanka-beaches-koggala.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>You should also make some time to watch the traditional practice of stilt fishing which is still in existence here. This is where the local fishermen sit high up on makeshift bamboo stilts, fishing in the waters close to the beach. They sit out there for hours under the blistering hot sun, showing tremendous strength and dedication to their work.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Koggala is also known among the Sri Lanka beaches as a good surfing spot, although the strong currents mean it&#x2019;s better for advanced surfers.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Koggala has a small rainforest reserve around a lake (close to the beach). Here you can discover mangroves, small islands, and an abundance of wildlife. Join a boat trip and learn more about nature.&#xA0;&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/sri-lanka-route-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sri Lanka Route Guide: a 3-week travel itinerary<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Season:<\/strong> December to April and July to September<\/li><li><strong>Crowded:<\/strong> Quiet<\/li><li><strong>Surfing:<\/strong> Good, better for advanced surfers. Quite windy, so it&#x2019;s also suitable for kitesurfing and windsurfing.<\/li><\/ul>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-8-arugam-bay\">8. Arugam Bay<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Arugam Bay, located on the east coast, is really the best of the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a> beaches for surfing, becoming more and more famous for surfers worldwide. In fact, there are even international surf competitions now held here. Because every day brings excellent waves, many surfers make Arugam Bay their home during the peak surfing period (April to September). <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/arugam-bay-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Arugam Bay Guide &#x2013; 7 x Things To Do<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art.jpg\" alt=\"sri lanka beaches arugam bay\"><\/noscript><img width=\"333\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sri lanka beaches arugam bay\" class=\"wp-image-6805 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1892px) 100vw, 1892px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art.jpg 1892w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art-300x304.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art-600x609.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art-333x338.jpg 333w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art-591x600.jpg 591w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art-798x810.jpg 798w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art-30x30.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art-161x163.jpg 161w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art-177x180.jpg 177w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-t