of the best national parks in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a>, like <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/yala-national-park\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Yala<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/elephants-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Udawalawe<\/a>. Because of this, you&#x2019;ll find lots of tour companies offering jeep safaris where you can spot elephants, monkeys, and even the elusive leopard!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Best time to visit:<\/strong> April until September (please note that some hotels will be closed outside of this primary surf season).<\/li><li><strong>Crowded:<\/strong> Popular in high-season<\/li><li><strong>Surfing:<\/strong> Best waves of all the Sri Lanka beaches!<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-view-elephant-rock.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"6789\" class=\"wp-image-6789 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155307\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-view-elephant-rock.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155307\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-view-elephant-rock-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155307\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-view-elephant-rock-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155307\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-view-elephant-rock-