nawatuna\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Awesome Things To Do in Unawatuna<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach.jpg\" alt=\"sri lanka beaches unawatuna main beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"305\" alt=\"sri lanka beaches unawatuna main beach\" class=\"wp-image-7371 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-300x203.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-600x406.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-450x305.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-800x542.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-1080x731.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-163x110.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-266x180.jpg 266w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-768x520.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-1024x693.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-1440x975.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23154431\/things-to-do-unawatuna-sri-lanka-beach.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>What&#x2019;s more, Unawatuna village has a laidback vibe, where days pass slowly in a haze of coconuts, good food, and refreshing morning swims. The beach is located in a sheltered bay, so it&#x2019;s very safe to swim in.&#xA0;&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Search for &#x2018;Dream Cabana&#x2019; in Unawatuna on Google Maps, and you&#x2019;ll find the Instagram hot spot of the town: an amazing beach swing hanging high from a long protruding palm tree on the beach.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Season:<\/strong> November to April<\/li><li><strong>Crowded:<\/strong> Popular in high-season as this part of the south coast is very accessible from Colombo.&#xA0;<\/li><li><strong>Surfing:<\/strong> Possible but not great. The sheltered bay is better for swimming and relaxing.<\/li><\/ul>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-10-hikkaduwa-beach\">10. Hikkaduwa Beach<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The beach of Hikkaduwa is one of the <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a> beaches located on the west coast and the closest to Colombo. Because of its west-facing nature, the sunsets at Hikkaduwa Beach are out of this world; nothing beats seeing the sun melt into the horizon line in the warm evening air.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/sri-lanka-beaches-hikkaduwa-turtles.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"7548\" class=\"wp-image-7548 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154051\/sri-lanka-beaches-hikkaduwa-turtles.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154051\/sri-lanka-beaches-hikkaduwa-turtles-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154051\/sri-lanka-beaches-hikkaduwa-turtles-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154051\/sri-lanka-beaches-hikkaduwa-turtles-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154051\/sri-lanka-beaches-hikkaduwa-turtles-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154051\/sri-lanka-beaches-hikkaduwa-turtles-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154051\/sri-lanka-beaches-hikkaduwa-turtles-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154051\/sri-lanka-beaches-hikkaduwa-turtles-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23154051\/sri-lanka-beaches-hikkaduwa-tu